Common fixings used in this design:
HEX6.3 = 6.3mm tapped hex = Jaycar.com.au part HP0920 or equivalent
M3x15 = M3x15mm screw = Jaycar.com.au part HP0407 or equivalent
M3x32 = M3x32mm screw = Jaycar.com.au part HP0418 or equivalent
HEX15 = 15mm tapped hex = Jaycar.com.au part HP0926 or equivalent
NUT+WASHER = Nylon NUT & WASHER = Jaycar.com.au part HP0150 or equivalent
NUT = M3 nylon nut = Jaycar.com.au part HP0146 or equivalent
M3x6 = M3x6mm screw = Jaycar.com.au part HP0400 or equivalent
HEX25 = M3x25 metal tappex hex = Jaycar.com.au part HP0907 or equivalent
